{
  "stem": "2735.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a rocky area, somewhere-- like some grass, but there were rocks in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember laying down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were all laying down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think it was somewhere close to a train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And people were-- it was summer night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Girls were going out with boys and laughing on dates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was music playing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was like there was no war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And here, we're already exhausted, going from one place to another one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother, as I told you in the beginning, she was a very fragile woman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She maybe weighed at 100 pounds.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she didn't complain-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was the first to go, the first to direct, the first to-- to help out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember feeling very sad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we came to a town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "From Kuybyshev, we came Zhytomyr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I hope I did not change the names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was a-- a gentile town-- a lot of Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Right away, I could see that they went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Meanwhile, I don't remember exactly where.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Or-- we met a family that we were very close with them, but I don't remember exactly where.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were not with them there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I think after Zhytomyr, we met them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was a mother and a father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was one daughter that was my age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we knew each other from that small town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And another daughter who was pregnant, her husband was-- that's another story what-- where her husband was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were clutching to each other, that we'll stay together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we came to a big city, Kharkiv.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And at Kharkiv, they told us they're going to send us to the middle Asia, like Samarkand or Tashkent-- some-- because it's warm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the Russian winter is very severe.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
